content: Cool app. Any way you could program gallons dev?
I love it but I would really like to see larger font or a setting to control the size.
The app is good and accurate, but it could use an update. When usung the app if the landscape of your phone changes it erases fuel data so turn off screen rotate when flying.

I was using this app and minimized it and when it came back on all my fuel stuff was deleted. it would be a 5 star rating if it wasnt for that. Also almost no one uses external takks anymore. An internal tank instead of external would be helpful. I want my money back!

This is a great app for me. I am a Crew Chief for the UH-60 Blackhawk and this saves me a lot of time in my crew station. It allows me to spend less time fidgeting with a calculator and more time focused outside. I highly recommend it. I do however have one con to mention; LOCK YOUR SCREEN ORIENTATION. If you do not, your fuel check timer will reset and you will need to start all over.
Bad App I payed in 11 February 19 until now 14 February 19 I can not download it .. Return my money .. 5 days and still pending installing
works perfectly for what its made for
